rows.label: tlk400906_msg0001
rows.name: Hmm? You want something?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0002
rows.name: Tora want to ask about Black Ash!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0003
rows.name:
About Black Ash, eh? Lemme guess -
Isset's been blabbing, has he?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0004
rows.name: That correct.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0005
rows.name: Honestly, that little punk...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0006
rows.name:
But hey, it's not like I'm doing anything
wrong. So sure, I'll tell you.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0007
rows.name: What d'you want to know?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0008
rows.name:
Have you been selling large quantities
of Black Ash to someone?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0009
rows.name:
I dunno if I'd call it that large.
Just a few barrels at a time,
every now and then.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0010
rows.name:
If using as shielding agent for ether
furnace, maybe not need such large
quantity all at once.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0011
rows.name: Oh, I see.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0012
rows.name:
So could you tell us where you're
delivering these barrels to?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0013
rows.name:
Near the entrance to the
Old Industrial District.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0014
rows.name:
I just drop the goods off where I'm
told to, so I haven't seen the buyer
or anything.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0015
rows.name: Sounds suspicious.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0016
rows.name: You reckon?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0017
rows.name:
They're reliable with their money,
and they pay a fair price. Can't say
I ever thought anything seemed off.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0018
rows.name:
And after all, if you're going to build
something outside the city, why bother
having it carried inside?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0019
rows.name:
Not to mention that meeting up in
person would mean having to schedule
a time that suits both people.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0020
rows.name: I guess that's a fair point, but still...

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0021
rows.name: When's your next delivery?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0022
rows.name: Ten days' time.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0023
rows.name: Seriously? We have to wait that long?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0024
rows.name:
Perhaps we should simply enjoy an
extended hot spring vacation.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0025
rows.name:
Would that not be...
less than productive?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0026
rows.name:
Well, I only just made the last
delivery. If you head there quick,
it might even still be there!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0027
rows.name: Tell us these things first!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0028
rows.name: Come on, guys, it's worth a try!

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0029
rows.name: Are the barrels easy to spot?

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0030
rows.name:
Yeah, they should be pretty obvious.
They're bright green, after all.

rows.label: tlk400906_msg0031
rows.name:
Lemme know if there's anything
else you want sorting out.
